## Supabase (public anon client keys)
# Get these from your Supabase project settings:
# Project Settings → API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY"

## Google Sheets – customer signups (checkout complete)
# Web app URL from Apps Script (Deploy → New deployment → Web app).
# See docs/google-sheets-customers.md for setup.
GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBAPP_URL="https://script.google.com/macros/s/YOUR_SCRIPT_ID/exec"
